し）」は、現代ではほぼ使われない「思う」の","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"である「思す（おぼす）」に「召す」を加えることで敬意を強めた言い方です","url":null},{"styles":["ref_num"],"text":"9","url":"#fn:9"},{"styles":[],"text":"。\n現代では敬意の強弱がほとんど出来ない","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"ですが、昔は「召す」によって可能でした。","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"\n\n","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"「","url":null},{"styles":["strong"],"text":"食べる","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"」「","url":null},{"styles":["strong"],"text":"飲む","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"」「","url":null},{"styles":["strong"],"text":"着る","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"」の","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"、と覚えれば十分なのですが、上述の理由から言葉に「召す」が入っている場合は","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"の可能性があります。\n（「召集」など、音読みの場合は反対に「目上の人が目下の人に対して行う」という意味が多いので当てはまりません）","url":null}],"type":"body"},{"text_items":[{"styles":[],"text":"まとめ","url":null}],"type":"h2"},{"text_items":[{"styles":[],"text":"本記事の","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"を覚えると、例えば「","url":null},{"styles":["strong"],"text":"話す","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"」を","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"にしたい場合、","url":null}],"type":"body"},{"list_items":[[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"おっしゃる","url":null}],[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"お話しくださる","url":null}],[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"話してくださる","url":null}],[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"話していらっしゃる","url":null}],[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"お話しなさる","url":null}],[{"styles":["strong"],"text":"お話しになる","url":null}]],"type":"num_list"},{"text_items":[{"styles":[],"text":"と、6通りもの言い方が出来るようになります。","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"\n\n","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"相手を高める言い回しを増やしたい方や、語彙を増やしたい方にお勧めの敬語です。","url":null},{"styles":[],"text":"\n\n","url":null},{"styles":["respectful"],"text":"尊敬語","url":null},{